            &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 贈票單位: {!Tickets.External_Tickets__r.Company__c} &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp;  &nbsp; 協辦單位: 星宇航空股份有限公司            
